.TH L10N-GLOSSARY 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "L10n Glossary Manual"
.SH NAME
l10n-glossary - Translation glossary editor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B l10n-glossary
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBl10n-glossary\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for creating and managing translation glossaries in TBX, CSV, and TSV formats. Features include adding, editing, and deleting terms with context and comments, importing terms from .po/.ts files, exporting to multiple formats, consistency checking against translation files, multi-language support, and glossary merging.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/l10n-glossary/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/l10n-glossary/
Cached data.
